      "title": "READ ME - models needed",
      "properties": {
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "Difforum: Native realtime (Live Sampler internal loop).\n\nQueue ONCE and watch the node stream a live preview as it generates - the\nLive Sampler keeps the model resident and loops warp + kaleidoscope +\n1-step re-diffuse internally. No external runtime.\n\nModels:\n- SD-Turbo -> models/checkpoints  (hf: stabilityai/sd-turbo)\n  or any SD1.5 + LCM-LoRA (hf: latent-consistency/lcm-lora-sdv1-5)\nUse 512x512, 1-2 steps, cfg 1. Add TensorRT + TAESD for max FPS.\n\nMagic mirror: set the Live Sampler's live_source to 0 (webcam) or a video\npath to stylize a live feed (kaleidoscope your camera). Needs opencv.\nLive output: set stream_dir (folder for OBS/Resolume) or spout_name\n(needs SpoutGL). See REALTIME.md."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    }
